  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/60ede64dcd0e4eea9407f7c8a7560808.poster.avif?t=1773451685\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/60ede64dcd0e4eea9407f7c8a7560808.webm?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/60ede64dcd0e4eea9407f7c8a7560808.mp4?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A desperate letter summons detective Paul Trilby to a peculiar island town, divided by a wall and ruled by a Hospital. Regular citizens get admitted and then return without their memories. A sinister conspiracy is afoot. Can you get to the bottom of this mystery?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the meaning is a surreal, hand-drawn, point-and-click adventure inspired by classic titles like Samorost and the Rusty Lake series.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/360d74bbd1f1f369ad285b42f77888f7.poster.avif?t=1773451685\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/360d74bbd1f1f369ad285b42f77888f7.webm?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/360d74bbd1f1f369ad285b42f77888f7.mp4?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use wit, curiosity and lateral thinking to puzzle your way towards a solution, helped by the citizens you meet along the way. Remember that there is always a grain of truth in the local gossip. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/2b9b7e9bf8bea5f39b3157787a5b4851.poster.avif?t=1773451685\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/2b9b7e9bf8bea5f39b3157787a5b4851.webm?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/2b9b7e9bf8bea5f39b3157787a5b4851.mp4?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short, strange, satisfying adventure for those in search of something different. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Hand-drawn art brings the offbeat world to life</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Whimsical worldbuilding with a sinister undertone</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Atmospheric soundtrack by Victor Butzelaar</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ A twisted mystery that awaits your diligent inspection</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 1.5 hours average playtime<br><br>🔎 You can already start <i>Paul_Trilby</i>'s investigation by visiting the Follow the meaning website (link in sidebar) 🖥️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/95a05888dad326eb12918415d47471dd.poster.avif?t=1773451685\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/95a05888dad326eb12918415d47471dd.webm?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/95a05888dad326eb12918415d47471dd.mp4?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/60ede64dcd0e4eea9407f7c8a7560808.poster.avif?t=1773451685\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/60ede64dcd0e4eea9407f7c8a7560808.webm?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/60ede64dcd0e4eea9407f7c8a7560808.mp4?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A desperate letter summons detective Paul Trilby to a peculiar island town, divided by a wall and ruled by a Hospital. Regular citizens get admitted and then return without their memories. A sinister conspiracy is afoot. Can you get to the bottom of this mystery?  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Follow the meaning is a surreal, hand-drawn, point-and-click adventure inspired by classic titles like Samorost and the Rusty Lake series.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/360d74bbd1f1f369ad285b42f77888f7.poster.avif?t=1773451685\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/360d74bbd1f1f369ad285b42f77888f7.webm?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/360d74bbd1f1f369ad285b42f77888f7.mp4?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use wit, curiosity and lateral thinking to puzzle your way towards a solution, helped by the citizens you meet along the way. Remember that there is always a grain of truth in the local gossip. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/2b9b7e9bf8bea5f39b3157787a5b4851.poster.avif?t=1773451685\" width=600 height=166 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/2b9b7e9bf8bea5f39b3157787a5b4851.webm?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/2b9b7e9bf8bea5f39b3157787a5b4851.mp4?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A short, strange, satisfying adventure for those in search of something different. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Hand-drawn art brings the offbeat world to life</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Whimsical worldbuilding with a sinister undertone</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ Atmospheric soundtrack by Victor Butzelaar</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ A twisted mystery that awaits your diligent inspection</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >■ 1.5 hours average playtime<br><br>🔎 You can already start <i>Paul_Trilby</i>'s investigation by visiting the Follow the meaning website (link in sidebar) 🖥️</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/95a05888dad326eb12918415d47471dd.poster.avif?t=1773451685\" width=600 height=180 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/95a05888dad326eb12918415d47471dd.webm?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2720280/extras/95a05888dad326eb12918415d47471dd.mp4?t=1773451685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
